{"id":129,"parent_id":124,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":129,"title":"Romans 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","Man is justified through the blood of Christ—Adam fell, and Christ atoned that man might be saved."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.1","order":"03.08.005.15347"},["b","1"],"Therefore being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"justified"],"by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"faith"],", we have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"peace"],"with God through our Lord Jesus Christ:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.2","order":"03.08.005.15348"},["b","2"],"By whom also we have access by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"faith"],"into this grace wherein we stand, and rejoice in hope of the glory of God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.3","order":"03.08.005.15349"},["b","3"],"And not only",["i","so,"],"but we glory in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"tribulations"],"also: knowing that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"tribulation"],"worketh",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"patience"],";"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.4","order":"03.08.005.15350"},["b","4"],"And patience, experience; and experience, hope:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.5","order":"03.08.005.15351"},["b","5"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"hope"],"maketh not ashamed; because the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"love"],"of God is shed abroad in our hearts by the Holy Ghost which is given unto us."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.6","order":"03.08.005.15352"},["b","6"],"For when we were yet without",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"strength"],", in due time Christ died for the ungodly."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.7","order":"03.08.005.15353"},["b","7"],"For scarcely for a righteous man will one die: yet peradventure for a good man some would even dare to die."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.8","order":"03.08.005.15354"},["b","8"],"But God commendeth his love toward us, in that, while we were yet",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"sinners"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"Christ"],"died for us."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.9","order":"03.08.005.15355"},["b","9"],"Much more then, being now",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"justified"],"by his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"blood"],", we shall be saved from wrath through him."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.10","order":"03.08.005.15356"},["b","10"],"For if, when we were enemies, we were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"reconciled"],"to God by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"death"],"of his Son, much more, being reconciled, we shall be saved by his life."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.11","order":"03.08.005.15357"},["b","11"],"And not only",["i","so,"],"but we also joy in God through our Lord Jesus Christ, by whom we have now received the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"atonement"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.12","order":"03.08.005.15358"},["b","12"],"Wherefore, as by one man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sin"],"entered into the world, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"death"],"by sin; and so",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"death"],"passed upon all men, for that all have",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"sinned"],":"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.13","order":"03.08.005.15359"},["b","13"],"(For until the law sin was in the world: but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sin"],"is not imputed when there is no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"law"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.14","order":"03.08.005.15360"},["b","14"],"Nevertheless death reigned from Adam to Moses, even over them that had not sinned after the similitude of Adam’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"transgression"],", who is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"figure"],"of him that was to come."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.15","order":"03.08.005.15361"},["b","15"],"But not as the offence, so also",["i","is"],"the free gift. For if through the offence of one many be dead, much more the grace of God, and the gift by grace,",["i","which is"],"by",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"one"],"man, Jesus Christ, hath abounded unto many."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.16","order":"03.08.005.15362"},["b","16"],"And not as",["i","it was"],"by one that sinned,",["i","so is"],"the gift: for the judgment",["i","was"],"by one to condemnation, but the free gift",["i","is"],"of many offences unto justification."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.17","order":"03.08.005.15363"},["b","17"],"For if by one man’s offence death reigned by one; much more they which receive abundance of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"grace"],"and of the gift of righteousness shall reign in life by one, Jesus Christ.)"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.18","order":"03.08.005.15364"},["b","18"],"Therefore as by the offence of one",["i","judgment came"],"upon all men to condemnation; even so by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"righteousness"],"of one",["i","the free gift came"],"upon all men unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"justification"],"of life."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.19","order":"03.08.005.15365"},["b","19"],"For as by one man’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"disobedience"],"many were made sinners, so by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"obedience"],"of one shall many be made righteous."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.20","order":"03.08.005.15366"},["b","20"],"Moreover the law entered, that the offence might abound. But where sin abounded, grace did much more abound:"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.21","order":"03.08.005.15367"},["b","21"],"That as sin hath reigned unto death, even so might grace reign through",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"righteousness"],"unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"eternal life"],"by Jesus Christ our Lord."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.1a","order":"03.08.005.15368"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justification"},"TG Justification"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.1b","order":"03.08.005.15370"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.1c","order":"03.08.005.15372"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"TG Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.2a","order":"03.08.005.15374"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/5.5.5-6"},"Gal. 5:5 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.3a","order":"03.08.005.15376"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.17"},"2 Cor. 4:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.3b","order":"03.08.005.15378"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/tribulation"},"TG Tribulation"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.3c","order":"03.08.005.15380"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/patience"},"TG Patience"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.5a","order":"03.08.005.15382"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.116"},"Ps. 119:116"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"TG Hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.5b","order":"03.08.005.15384"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.6a","order":"03.08.005.15386"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.8a","order":"03.08.005.15388"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.11"},"Mosiah 4:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.8b","order":"03.08.005.15390"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-plan-of"},"TG Salvation, Plan of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.9a","order":"03.08.005.15392"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.9b","order":"03.08.005.15394"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-symbolism-of"},"TG Blood, Symbolism of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.10a","order":"03.08.005.15396"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"},"TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reconciliation"},"Reconciliation"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.10b","order":"03.08.005.15398"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-death-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Death of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.11a","order":"03.08.005.15400"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"reconciliation, restoration to favor.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/redemption"},"Redemption"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.12a","order":"03.08.005.15402"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/3.6"},"Gen. 3:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fall-of-man"},"TG Fall of Man"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.12b","order":"03.08.005.15404"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.21"},"1 Cor. 15:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/5.12c","order":"03.08.005.15406"},